statements: SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data WHERE user_id = 123;
SELECT page_url, duration_seconds FROM website_traffic_data WHERE entry_timestamp >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT visit_id, page_url, entry_timestamp, exit_timestamp FROM website_traffic_data WHERE duration_seconds > 60;
SELECT page_url, user_id FROM website_traffic_data WHERE exit_timestamp < '2022-06-01' ORDER BY entry_timestamp DESC;
SELECT AVG(duration_seconds) as average_duration FROM website_traffic_data WHERE user_id IN (456, 789);
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data WHERE user_id = 123 ORDER BY entry_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT visit_id, page_url, entry_timestamp FROM website_traffic_data WHERE duration_seconds > 60 ORDER BY exit_timestamp ASC;
SELECT user_id, entry_timestamp, exit_timestamp, duration_seconds FROM website_traffic_data WHERE page_url LIKE '%/products/%' AND exit_timestamp IS NOT NULL;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT user_id) AS unique_users, AVG(duration_seconds) AS avg_duration FROM website_traffic_data GROUP BY page_url HAVING COUNT(visit_id) > 5 ORDER BY avg_duration DESC;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(visit_id) AS visit_count, MAX(duration_seconds) AS max_duration FROM website_traffic_data GROUP BY user_id HAVING visit_count > 3 ORDER BY max_duration DESC;

SELECT website_visits.page_url, referrer_sources.referrer_name, marketing_campaigns.campaign_name FROM website_visits LEFT JOIN referrer_sources ON website_visits.visitor_id = referrer_sources.referrer_id INNER JOIN marketing_campaigns ON website_visits.visitor_id = marketing_campaigns.campaign_id;
